# Traffic Sign Detection Dataset

This dataset is designed for training and evaluating a YOLOv8-based model for traffic sign detection. Traffic sign detection is a crucial task in autonomous driving systems, advanced driver-assistance systems (ADAS), and smart city applications. This dataset aims to provide a comprehensive collection of annotated images for various types of traffic signs commonly found in urban and highway environments.
